{
  "stem": "3988.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So maybe 5 o'clock, maybe 6 o'clock in the morning, we heard by the window we were sleeping, the Polish cavalry, you know, on horses, you know, dressed up in uniforms and with the bayonets or the guns, were going towards the German border.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, so we know something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we just get sleeping, and you know, like nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But maybe a couple hours later or something, we heard them running back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were running back and the Germans' tank coming in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were going fighting with the horses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And here the German army came in with tanks and machine guns, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I run out of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was right there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wanted to see a war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I heard fighting, shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And because I learned that in school, you know, history, you know, about wars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I said, oh, here I'm-- I'll see a war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time I think I was about 12, you know, something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother grabbed me, you know, bullets flying all over the place, grabbed me, and pulled me in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed maybe a couple hours in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans start coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in back of the house, we had a cellar.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we never-- that's how we kept our food if something was left over, you know, the day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to wrap it in rags, you know, and the pot, you know, and the rag, you know, and put a stone on top of it, or-- or a brick.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you put it in the cellar, you know, to keep it cool.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
